title: Celtic Dreamtime - Album
description:
Celtic Dreamtime album from Reflections Music.

CD Rips outputted to both FLAC and MP3 320kbps.

Produced and arranged by Jeff Victor. All songs composed by Jeff Victor, except Track #10 (Traditional).

"Reflections presents music and video that suit your lifestyle. With a wide range of genres to choose from, the line feature captivating music and breathtaking video you'll enjoy again and again."

Tracklist:

1. I Am Ireland
2. Pipe Dream
3. The Mermaid's Tears
4. Mise Eire
5. One Yellow Rose
6. Overture
7. Letter To A Lost Love
8. The Emerald Isle
9. She Wove A Cloak Of Many Yarns
10. The Rose Of Tralee/Danny Boy

Enjoy.
